Tirmit-iw akked waṭṭan n teskiẓufrinit.
Yiwen n wass deg wussan n tegrest mi lliɣ ḍelqeɣ ɣef wussu.
Ḥulfaɣ i uḍar-iw yettembiwil.
Selleɣ i kra n leṣwat ixelḍen tteffɣen-d seg wallaɣ-iw.
Uqbel Aseggas ɣer deffir iyi-d-yebda kullec.
Taɣawsa akk tamezwarut i ibeddlen deg tudert-iw d iḍes.
