Wid d-iheddren yid-i.
Mi ara yi-d-yini umɛellem-iw xdem aya neɣ aya.
Tafyirt-nni ur ssawaḍeɣ ara ad tt-fehmeɣ alma zziɣ-tt acḥal n yiberdan deg wallaɣ-iw.
